      "content": "that's exactly what i'm afraid of. it feels like these claims can just come out of nowhere and ruin everything. is there any way to limit my liability or make the clause less \"all or nothing\"? like, can i negotiate it so i'm only responsible if i actually did something wrong on purpose?",
